)$\\rangle$. Experimental results show that BiVE significantly\noutperforms all other methods in the two new tasks and the typical base-level\nlink prediction in real-world bi-level knowledge graphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2023 07:45:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 09:12:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2023 16:30:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
