ellent agreement was obtained for two\nrecent potentials. However, these potentials cannot reproduce literature data\nfor the 144Sm(a,g)148Gd reaction with the same accuracy. Constraints for the\nAOMP were derived from an analysis of the new 144Sm(a,n)147Gd data and\nliterature data for 144Sm(a,g)148Gd. These constraints enable a determination\nof the reaction rate of the 144Sm(a,g)148Gd reaction with significantly reduced\nuncertainties of less than a factor of two.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2023 10:53:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-22"}
