nce detection methods. Our model also contributes to the field of\nbenchmark networks more generally by enabling further exploration of the\nability of new and existing methods to detect ambiguity in mesoscale structure\nof networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2023 14:02:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-07"}
